    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;The Optimized Link State Routing Protocol version 2 (OLSRv2) includes the ability to assign metrics to links and to use those metrics to allow routing by other than minimum hop count routes.  This document provides a historic record of the rationale for, and design considerations behind, how link metrics were included in OLSRv2.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
